text: Goephanes obliquepictus is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was first described by Léon Fairmaire in 1903.Biolib.cz - Goephanes. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Goephanes Category:Beetles described in 1903 Category:Taxa named by Léon Fairmaire
